							</ul>
							<a href="#" class="close">Close</a>
						</div>
					</nav>

				<!-- Banner -->
					<section id="banner">
						<div class="inner">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="https://salvium.io/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anim-salvium-WHT.gif" alt="Salvium Animation">
        </div>
							<h2>Take The Green Pill</h2>
							<p>Privacy isn't just a feature. It's fundamental.</p>
						</div>
					</section>

				<!-- Wrapper -->
					<section id="wrapper">

						<!-- One -->
							<section id="one" class="wrapper spotlight style1">
								<div class="inner">
									<a href="#" class="image"><img src="images/pic01.jpg" alt="" /></a>
									<div class="content">
										<h2 class="major">Privacy's Next Chapter</h2>
										<p>Combining proven privacy technology with native staking and DeFi capabilities. True financial privacy meets programmable yield.</p>
										<a href="#" class="special">Learn more</a>
									</div>
								</div>
							</section>

						<!-- Two -->
							<section id="two" class="wrapper alt spotlight style2">
								<div class="inner">
									<a href="#" class="image"><img src="images/pic02.jpg" alt="" /></a>
									<div class="content">
										<h2 class="major">Stake in the Shadows</h2>
										<p>Generate yield without exposing your position. Because financial privacy is a fundamental right.</p>
										<a href="#" class="special">Learn more</a>
									</div>
								</div>
							</section>

						<!-- Three -->
							<section id="three" class="wrapper spotlight style3">
								<div class="inner">
									<a href="#" class="image"><img src="images/pic03.jpg" alt="" /></a>
									<div class="content">
										<h2 class="major">Privacy Meets Progress</h2>
										<p>First protocol to unite battle-tested privacy with DeFi's innovation, built for long-term sustainability in an evolving regulatory landscape.</p>
										<a href="#" class="special">Learn more</a>
									</div>
								</div>
							</section>

						<!-- Four -->
							<section id="four" class="wrapper alt style1">
								<div class="inner">
									<h2 class="major">The Evolution of Private Finance</h2>
									<p>Built on battle-tested privacy foundations to unlock the future of DeFi. Created by privacy believers, for a future where financial sovereignty and DeFi innovation coexist.</p>
									<section class="features">
										<article>
											<a href="#" class="image"><img src="images/pic04.jpg" alt="" /></a>
											<h3 class="major">Private DeFi</h3>
											<p>True financial privacy meets programmable smart contracts, enabling a new generation of private financial applications.</p>
											<a href="#" class="special">Learn more</a>
										</article>
										<article>
											<a href="#" class="image"><img src="images/pic05.jpg" alt="" /></a>
											<h3 class="major">Native Staking</h3>
											<p>Earn rewards while maintaining complete privacy. Your financial moves should be yours alone.</p>
											<a href="#" class="special">Learn more</a>
										</article>
										<article>
											<a href="#" class="image"><img src="images/pic06.jpg" alt="" /></a>
											<h3 class="major">Regulatory Ready</h3>
											<p>Built for long-term sustainability with features that enable compliance without compromising core privacy.</p>
											<a href="#" class="special">Learn more</a>
										</article>
										<article>
											<a href="#" class="image"><img src="images/pic07.jpg" alt="" /></a>
											<h3 class="major">Beyond Private</h3>
											<p>Not just private transactions - a complete ecosystem for building the future of private finance.</p>
											<a href="#" class="special">Learn more</a>
										</article>
									</section>
									<ul class="actions">
										<li><a href="#" class="button">Join the Evolution</a></li>
									</ul>
								</div>
							</section>

					</section>

				<!-- Footer -->
					<section id="footer">
						<div class="inner">
							<h2 class="major">Join the Movement</h2>
							<p>In a world demanding both privacy and programmability, we're expanding what's possible. Not by replacing what works, but by building upon it.</p>
							<form method="post" action="#">
								<div class="fields">
									<div class="field">
										<label for="name">Name</label>
										<input type="text" name="name" id="name" />
									</div>
									<div class="field">
										<label for="email">Email</label>
										<input type="email" name="email" id="email" />
									</div>
									<div class="field">
										<label for="message">Message</label>
										<textarea name="message" id="message" rows="4"></textarea>
									</div>
								</div>
								<ul class="actions">
									<li><input type="submit" value="Send Message" /></li>
								</ul>
							</form>
							<ul class="contact">
								<li class="icon solid fa-home">Salvium Protocol</li>
								<li class="icon brands fa-discord"><a href="https://discord.gg/YJmdGcdtDt">Discord</a></li>
								<li class="icon brands fa-twitter"><a href="https://x.com/salvium_io">X.com</a></li>
								<li class="icon brands fa-github"><a href="https://github.com/somerandomcryptoguy/salvium">GitHub</a></li>
							</ul>
